            "notes": "The main concept of this deck is to control the game through a combination of counterspells, removal, and card advantage. Tasigur, the Golden Fang serves as the commander, allowing the player to repeatedly delve deep into their graveyard for powerful spells. The deck includes a variety of counterspells like Mana Leak and Force of Negation to disrupt opponents' plans, along with removal spells such as Fatal Push and Dismember to deal with threats. Card advantage is also key, with cards like Tamiyo, Inquisitive Student and Snapcaster Mage allowing the player to draw cards and reuse spells. By effectively controlling the game and out-valuing opponents, this deck aims to outlast and outmaneuver its opponents to secure victory."
